<h2>Visual Identity</h2>
<p>The project keeps a compact and readable game interface while using the SVG assets to preserve a hand-made arcade look.</p>
<table>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Style</strong><br>Clean arcade presentation</td>
    <td><strong>Motion</strong><br>Storm, lightning, and impact feedback</td>
    <td><strong>Audio</strong><br>Background music plus stronger hit sounds</td>
  </tr>
</table>

