<hr>

<h2>How to Run</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Open the project folder in VS Code.</li>
  <li>Use Live Server on <code>index.html</code>, or open the file directly in a browser.</li>
  <li>No build step is required.</li>
</ol>

<hr>

<h2>Controls</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Mouse click: eliminate enemies and collect power-ups</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Status</h2>
<p>The project is playable and organized into modular JavaScript, CSS, and asset files.</p>
